      <div class="msgContentFrame">Iron Spear head attemptable at r30 BSM, Iron Lance Head at r36, from what the BSMs told me. Iron Spear Butt is as low as r22, or even lower, Iron Spear Clasp is about r15. You need a r27 CRP to be able to put them together. But the Iron Spear has worse stat than the Brass Spear until r23 LNC. Supposedly the Feathered Harpoon would have been a r19 weapon (Harpoon - 9, Tortoiseshell - 29, Yarzonshell - 39) but somehow SE decided to make it a r14 for no reason.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1807831.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
